+# Exploration 002 Report - Comparator Dynamic Audit
+
+## Goal
+
+Audit the Step-3 comparators `vorticity-direction coherence` and `tube coherence / persistence` against the fixed Step-3 package:
+
+- primary scenario: filament or tube concentration
+- comparator scenario: sheet or pancake concentration
+- localization: Eulerian parabolic package on `B_r(x_*) x [t_* - r^2, t_*]`
+- threshold: `|omega| >= r^{-2}`
+
+Required outputs:
+
+- best available transport identity or propagation heuristic
+- main diffusion loss
+- main localization-evolution or commutator burden
+- dependence on the fixed package
+- Tao discriminator status
+- first obvious failure mode
+- final dynamic rating for each comparator
+
+## Method
+
+- Read the required Step-2, Step-3, Step-4, chain, and library source anchors.
+- Extract the strongest source-based dynamic story available for each comparator.
+- Record where dynamic persistence fails under the fixed Eulerian package.
+- Compare each comparator against the Step-3 primary hybrid without importing hidden derivative control or tube-adapted relocalization.
+
+## Running Notes
+
+### Initial scaffold
+
+[VERIFIED] Report skeleton created before analysis. Findings appended below as sources are read.
+
+### Operational note
+
+- The launched explorer produced the scaffold above but did not complete the
+  analysis in time. The strategizer completed the source-based audit directly
+  from the anchored local materials so the step could continue.
+
+## Findings
+
+### 1. Comparator: `vorticity-direction coherence`
+
+#### Best available transport or propagation story
+
+- [VERIFIED] The local record treats this route as genuinely stretching-facing
+  but already heavily overlapped with Constantin-Fefferman-style criteria and
+  later direction-coherence work. Sources:
+  - `library/factual/geometry-route-screening/direction-regularity-is-prior-art-not-a-standalone-novelty-claim.md`
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-002/explorations/exploration-001/REPORT.md`
+- [INFERRED] The best available dynamic story is the normalized-vorticity one:
+  if `xi = omega / |omega|` remains coherent on the intense set, then the local
+  stretching factor `xi . S xi` stays geometrically meaningful and may later
+  reduce a stretching contribution in a fixed representation. Sources:
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/MISSION.md`
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-003/RESULTS.md`
+  - `library/factual/geometry-route-screening/geometry-candidates-must-act-on-full-stretching.md`
+- [INFERRED] But the local repository does not supply a new propagation bridge
+  beyond that heuristic. It does not identify a theorem-level transport law for
+  localized direction coherence on the neutral Eulerian intense set.
+
+#### Main diffusion loss
+
+- [INFERRED] Diffusion acts directly on the normalized field through derivative
+  terms, so controlling `xi` dynamically is stricter than merely keeping
+  `|omega|` large on `E_r(t)`.
+- [VERIFIED] The repository already warns that the route too easily smuggles in
+  stronger `nabla xi` control than the observable package provides. Sources:
+  - `library/factual/geometry-route-screening/direction-regularity-is-prior-art-not-a-standalone-novelty-claim.md`
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-003/RESULTS.md`
+
+#### Main localization-evolution or commutator burden
+
+- [INFERRED] The direction field must be measured on the moving Eulerian
+  superlevel set `E_r(t)`, so one pays both the superlevel-set evolution burden
+  and the usual cutoff cost of a parabolic localization.
+- [INFERRED] The practical burden is not just transport but keeping the same
+  direction-coherence notion meaningful across the window without replacing it
+  by a stronger regularity norm that already belongs to prior-art criteria.
+
+#### Dependence on the fixed package
+
+- [INFERRED] This comparator depends most on the intensity threshold staying
+  strong enough that `xi` is meaningful but weak enough that the route does not
+  amount to hand-picked regions with unusually regular direction.
+
+#### Tao discriminator status
+
+- [VERIFIED] As a standalone route, its Tao discriminator is weak because the
+  local corpus already treats direction coherence as benchmark material unless a
+  new NS-specific bridge to full stretching or persistence is supplied. Sources:
+  - `library/factual/geometry-route-screening/direction-regularity-is-prior-art-not-a-standalone-novelty-claim.md`
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-002/explorations/exploration-002/REPORT.md`
+
+#### First obvious failure mode
+
+- [INFERRED] The first failure mode is immediate collapse into a known
+  direction-regularity criterion after importing stronger `nabla xi` control
+  than the fixed Step-3 package contains.
+
+#### Final rating
+
+- [INFERRED] `informative but dynamically weak`
+
+### 2. Comparator: `tube coherence / persistence`
+
+#### Best available transport or propagation story
+
+- [VERIFIED] The local record repeatedly says this family is only live as a
+  dynamic or hybrid route; static tube language is not enough. Sources:
+  - `library/factual/geometry-route-screening/tube-persistence-remains-live-only-as-a-dynamic-or-hybrid-route.md`
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-002/explorations/exploration-001/REPORT.md`
+- [INFERRED] The best available story is a vortex-structure heuristic:
+  intense filamentary components might persist approximately because vorticity
+  is advected and stretched, so coherent tubes can survive long enough to keep
+  a later full-stretching term organized.
+- [INFERRED] But the local repository gives no exact transport law for
+  connected components of the Eulerian superlevel sets, and no theorem-level
+  persistence criterion for a tube family on the fixed package.
+
+#### Main diffusion loss
+
+- [INFERRED] Because the time window is one diffusion-scale interval, the tube
+  boundary itself is unstable at the scale used to define it. The strongest
+  visible risk is component merging, splitting, or threshold erosion.
+
+#### Main localization-evolution or commutator burden
+
+- [VERIFIED] Step 3 intentionally avoided tube-adapted localization, so this
+  comparator must track coherent intense components inside a neutral Eulerian
+  package. Sources:
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-003/RESULTS.md`
+  - `library/factual/geometry-route-screening/step-3-should-start-with-a-neutral-eulerian-parabolic-localization-package.md`
+- [INFERRED] That means the decisive burden is component matching:
+  without re-centering or fitting a tube axis, "the same tube persists" is not
+  a given fact but the missing dynamic content itself.
+
+#### Dependence on the fixed package
+
+- [INFERRED] This comparator depends most on the threshold and connectedness
+  rule. Small changes in threshold or time window can change whether the same
+  intense component even exists, which is exactly why Step 3 treated threshold
+  and window perturbations as overfit checks.
+
+#### Tao discriminator status
+
+- [VERIFIED] The Tao discriminator is real only if there is genuine
+  time/scale persistence; one-time coherent-structure language is Tao-robust
+  and therefore dead as a promoted route. Sources:
+  - `library/factual/geometry-route-screening/tube-persistence-remains-live-only-as-a-dynamic-or-hybrid-route.md`
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-002/explorations/exploration-002/REPORT.md`
+
+#### First obvious failure mode
+
+- [INFERRED] The first obvious failure mode is descriptive slippage:
+  tube language survives only after treating visually filamentary snapshots as
+  if they were a persistence mechanism, or after quietly switching to a
+  tube-adapted relocalization that the fixed Step-3 package disallows.
+
+#### Final rating
+
+- [INFERRED] `informative but dynamically weak`
+
+### 3. Comparator comparison
+
+- [INFERRED] Neither comparator outperforms the primary hybrid.
+- [INFERRED] `vorticity-direction coherence` is dynamically cleaner but more
+  obviously collapses into prior art once stronger derivative control appears.
+- [INFERRED] `tube coherence / persistence` carries the sharper Tao-sensitive
+  intuition but has the weaker transport law; under the fixed Eulerian package
+  it remains too close to descriptive tube language.
+- [INFERRED] Together they explain why the primary hybrid existed in the first
+  place:
+  - direction coherence is needed to stay pointed at stretching rather than at
+    geometry alone;
+  - tube persistence is needed so the route says something Tao-sensitive rather
+    than merely restating known direction-regularity criteria.
+- [INFERRED] Even so, combining two dynamically weak comparators does not yet
+  produce a dynamically plausible route on the fixed Step-3 package.
+
+## Dead Ends / Failed Attempts
+
+- [VERIFIED] No local theorem-level source was found that propagates localized
+  direction coherence on the fixed Eulerian package without stronger
+  `nabla xi`-type assumptions.
+- [VERIFIED] No local theorem-level source was found that transports connected
+  components of the thresholded intense set as a coherent tube family across
+  `[t_* - r^2, t_*]`.
+
+## Provisional Status
+
+- [INFERRED] Final ratings:
+  - `vorticity-direction coherence`:
+    `informative but dynamically weak`
+  - `tube coherence / persistence`:
+    `informative but dynamically weak`
+- [INFERRED] Comparator verdict:
+  neither comparator is dynamically stronger than the primary hybrid, and each
+  mainly clarifies one half of the hybrid's weakness.

