+- [INFERRED] But the local repository gives no exact transport law for
+  connected components of the Eulerian superlevel sets, and no theorem-level
+  persistence criterion for a tube family on the fixed package.
+
+#### Main diffusion loss
+
+- [INFERRED] Because the time window is one diffusion-scale interval, the tube
+  boundary itself is unstable at the scale used to define it. The strongest
+  visible risk is component merging, splitting, or threshold erosion.
+
+#### Main localization-evolution or commutator burden
+
+- [VERIFIED] Step 3 intentionally avoided tube-adapted localization, so this
+  comparator must track coherent intense components inside a neutral Eulerian
+  package. Sources:
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-003/RESULTS.md`
+  - `library/factual/geometry-route-screening/step-3-should-start-with-a-neutral-eulerian-parabolic-localization-package.md`
+- [INFERRED] That means the decisive burden is component matching:
+  without re-centering or fitting a tube axis, "the same tube persists" is not
+  a given fact but the missing dynamic content itself.
+
+#### Dependence on the fixed package
+
+- [INFERRED] This comparator depends most on the threshold and connectedness
+  rule. Small changes in threshold or time window can change whether the same
+  intense component even exists, which is exactly why Step 3 treated threshold
+  and window perturbations as overfit checks.
+
+#### Tao discriminator status
+
+- [VERIFIED] The Tao discriminator is real only if there is genuine
+  time/scale persistence; one-time coherent-structure language is Tao-robust
+  and therefore dead as a promoted route. Sources:
+  - `library/factual/geometry-route-screening/tube-persistence-remains-live-only-as-a-dynamic-or-hybrid-route.md`
+  - `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-002/explorations/exploration-002/REPORT.md`
+
+#### First obvious failure mode
+
