+- [VERIFIED] The package is fixed to the neutral Eulerian parabolic audit
+  region
+  `Q_r(x_*, t_*) = B_r(x_*) x [t_* - r^2, t_*]`
+  with intense set
+  `E_r(t) = {x in B_r(x_*) : |omega(x,t)| >= r^{-2}}`.
+  Sources:
